判不會介入球證在場上所作的判決，雙方也不會保持聯繫。"},{"pid":"221dd91e7bff686303d8acc28716bdbd7f44dca8","tid":807854,"uid":3747,"like":22,"dislike":3,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T01:20:12.000Z","msg":"航尼終於唔洗畀垃圾妓逼害"},{"pid":"1d60ba7a24e43d4941b99fdf9ac7b60663b6d1e7","tid":807854,"uid":372,"like":44,"dislike":3,"score":41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T01:22:38.000Z","msg":"抽水咪抽水囉，扮中立真係自己攞黎柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"845bbba4c6d759cff6344580aa1d3a3cfd0569cb","tid":807854,"uid":80456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T01:24:08.000Z","msg":"今季英超試用VAR，只會作為技術性測試，視像助理裁判不會介入球證在場上所作的判決，雙方也不會保持聯繫。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17770562fc9621d1fa58ef31cf566a47447f8965","tid":807854,"uid":33497,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T01:24:17.000Z","msg":"樓主抽水唔認死全家吧！"},{"pid":"947af1846c6849180aa918a91852ad14cdb863c3","tid":807854,"uid":11512,"like":3,"dislike":15,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T01:25:16.000Z","msg":"巧惡惡哦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f5b32883cf757862f690ec9ca993d906461b90c","tid":807854,"uid":15477,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T01:28:11.000Z","msg":"在俄羅斯世界盃決賽一役，法國取得領先的重要入球正是VAR的傑作。當時的球證在翻看視像後，判罰克羅地亞的比列錫犯手球，法國得到十二碼。<span style=\"color: red;\">這個判決在賽後受到球評家、名宿以至現役名將批評，指出比列錫的動作不屬蓄意手球，而且當時這球來勢很近，比列錫難以閃避，依球例不應判罰。</span><br />\n<br />\n嗰時好撚多傻鳩仲死撐話睇晒慢鏡比列錫一定係有心手球<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fce6bfff44afbede0a15333cff229b540d7f121","tid":807854,"uid":34490,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"845bbba4c6d759cff6344580aa1d3a3cfd0569cb","tid":807854,"uid":80456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T01:24:08.000Z